snippet.title: The Sims 4 Luxury Party Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Throw a luxurious party and add a touch of style to your Sims’ lives with The Sims 4 Luxury Party Stuff, available now!
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://o.ea.com/38637

Includes the all-new banquet table and fountain centerpiece that offers new gameplay experiences.

#sims4
